    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>10th-level Path of the Beast feature</i></p><p>When you hit a creature with your natural weapons while you are raging, the beast within you can curse your target with rabid fury. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw (DC equal to 8 + your Constitution modifier + your proficiency bonus) or suffer one of the following effects (your choice):</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">The target must use its reaction to make a melee attack against another creature of your choice that you can see.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">The target takes [[/damage 2d12 type=psychic]] damage.</li></ul><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
